# Trivy waiver list — add CVE IDs to silence them, with a justification
# and an expiry date in YYYY-MM-DD form.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-XXXX-YYYY  # rationale, expiry: YYYY-MM-DD
#
# Anything in this file MUST have an expiry date so we revisit. CVEs with
# an expired waiver should pop back into the failing gate at the next CI
# run — we treat the failure as a forcing function to either patch or
# document the new rationale.
